'''D. Vinayachandran''' is a well-known [[India]]n [[Malayalam]] poet. He is one of the proponents of modern style of prose in Malayalam poetry. 

== Awards ==

*Asan Smaraka Kavitha Puraskaram (Prize for Poetry) 2006<ref>{{cite web
|url=http://www.hindu.com/2006/10/15/stories/2006101509980400.htm
|title=Vinayachandran receives Asan award
|date=2006-10-15}}
</ref>.
*[[Kerala Sahithya Academy]] award ([[1983]]) - for his work titled 'Narakam Oru Premakatha' (A love story titled hell). <ref> http://www.dcbooks.com/Kerala.htm</ref>

==Published works==
{{incomplete}}
* Edasseriyude Thiranjedutha Kavithakal [[1996]] (This is a selection of poems written by Edasseri, hand picked by Vinayachandran). 
* Narakam Oru Premakatha (A Love story titled hell). 

